= ImageRuby-c - C-Extension replacement for color_replace! and draw! methods

Reimplements draw! and color_replace! methods of ImageRuby::Image class in C to make these operations 100X faster. 
draw and color_replace method are also affected because they use  draw! and color_replace!

== Installation

=== Gem installation

sudo gem install imageruby-c

== Usage

No explicit require is needed. Only with the gem installed, imageruby will include this improvement automagically
  
